trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.
trans-unit.target: Kall `Dispose` når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden forlater den <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall `Dispose`, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>ble bruker.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> </xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall `Dispose` før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>
